    >,
    player_actions: Array<
      {
        action_type_id: I32,
        layer: Base({ })
        | UpperBody({ }),
        allowed_concurrent_action_ids: Array<I32>
      }
    >,
    distant_visibile_entities: Array<
      {
        id: I32,
        entity_type: None({ })
        | Player({ })
        | Enemy({ })
        | Building({ })
        | Npc({ })
        | Resource({ }),
        description_id: I32
      }
    >,
    player_housing: Array<
      {
        secondary_knowledge_id: I32,
        rank: I32,
        name: String,
        template_building_id: I32
      }
    >,
    hexite_exchange_entries: Array<
      {
        id: I32,
        image_address: String,
        shard_amount: U32,
        base_shard_amount: U32,
        name: String,
        price: F32,
        event_name: String
      }
    >,
    reserved_name: Array<
      {
        name: String
      }
    >,
    contribution_loot: Array<
      {
        id: I32,
        enemy_type_id: I32,
        item_list_id: I32,
        minimum_contribution: I32,
        weighted: Bool
      }
    >
  }
}
